### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Test all scopes at once
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/demo
Accept: application/json

### Test Singleton Scope
# Run this multiple times - you should see the same ID but incrementing counter
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/singleton
Accept: application/json

### Test Request Scope
# Run this multiple times - you should see different IDs each time
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/request
Accept: application/json

### Test Session Scope
# Run this multiple times - you should see the same ID within the same session
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/session
Accept: application/json

### Test Application Scope
# Run this multiple times - you should see the same ID across all requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/application
Accept: application/json

### Test Session Scope in a new session
# Copy this request to a new file to test with a different session
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/session
Accept: application/json
Cookie: JSESSIONID=new_session_1

### Test multiple requests in sequence to verify scope behaviors

### 1. First Request - Note the IDs and counters
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/demo
Accept: application/json

### 2. Second Request - Compare with first request
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/demo
Accept: application/json

### 3. Third Request with new session
GET {{baseUrl}}/scopes/demo
Accept: application/json
Cookie: JSESSIONID=new_session_2

### Expected behaviors:
# - Singleton: Same ID, incrementing counter
# - Prototype: Different IDs each time
# - Request: Different IDs each request
# - Session: Same ID within same session, different across sessions
# - Application: Same ID across all requests

